{"tid":2435984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府刪改　香港史前文化沒受外來影響=>香港史前文化同受中原影響","createTime":"2021-03-06T17:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T01:41:10.000Z","uid":261647,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a516cfd2af15a714938ff1c990fda922545ac62b","tid":2435984,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3879801245409905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F3879801245409905&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3f0ad4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3879801245409905</a><br />\n<br />\n由1997年至2016年期間，年報一直都話史前文化係「在本土逐漸形成，並沒有受到外來文化重大影響」；但喺2017年呢句話就消失，取而代之嘅係香港文化「同樣受到中原文化影響」。年報本來有「香港的華人只求不受干擾，故在港英政府的開明統治下，均能安居樂業。」一句，但都喺17年打後嘅版本被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgbFUET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgbFUET.png&h=b062c06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5759&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3113ca4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5759</a><br />\n<br />\n最近董建華編修《香港志》，被質疑謬誤甚多，係要改造歷史迎合中共政權。有研究發現，由官方出版嘅《香港年報》本來一直都描述香港嘅史前文化「沒有受到外來重大影響」，但自2017年起，就篡改做「同樣受到中原文化影響」。<br />\n<br />\n[img]ttps://<a href=\"http://i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/未命名-4.png?w=814&amp;ssl=1[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-4.png%3Fw%3D814%26ssl%3D1%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=c12a4f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/未命名-4.png?w=814&amp;ssl=1[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報中文網》喺＜香港政府利用歷史灌輸愛國主義和忠誠＞嘅報道指出，喺政府年報「歷史」一章都會喺6000年前嘅考古遺迹講起。由1997年至2016年期間，年報一直都話史前文化係「在本土逐漸形成，並沒有受到外來文化重大影響」；但喺2017年呢句話就消失，取而代之嘅係香港文化「同樣受到中原文化影響」。年報本來有「香港的華人只求不受干擾，故在港英政府的開明統治下，均能安居樂業。」一句，但都喺17年打後嘅版本被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n[img]ttps://<a href=\"http://i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/未命名-2.png?w=693&amp;ssl=1[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-2.png%3Fw%3D693%26ssl%3D1%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=ba645222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/未命名-2.png?w=693&amp;ssl=1[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"b6605a2e3c35a3a2d1d5d6d8eaa2e9f474ce665e","tid":2435984,"uid":137038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"所以歷史博物館咪要「更新」囉<br />\n不過嗰陣大部份趁墟去嘅人都係on99咁，唔知「史前時期的香港」嗰部分都係會重點改造"},{"pid":"251bc4034edaac0bd360e5f1a034ca2cb12424a2","tid":2435984,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"好撚肉酸呀 支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb4f8285c5c69fe2bc50b95c02c7f80ba983464","tid":2435984,"uid":179409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"一貫手法，不斷改歷史講大話。"},{"pid":"6c86dd5064924b163ca00fd662018ff6e85a6166","tid":2435984,"uid":273218,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"廣州南粵王墓完全證明左香港自古係百越之地<br />\n歷史載海洋民族蜑家人<br />\n先係最古老民族<br />\n但港共政權完全無視<br />\n只強調客家同閩族<br />\n但偏偏客閩其實都係百越<br />\n客即係山客=輋<br />\n香港和峯坪輋大量證明<br />\n係都要放大小數係珠璣巷南來漢人歷史<br />\n其中重要有一大部分係本地人扮漢人"},{"pid":"44219d6e7e98ee91797b562a1ce7129ecc19fe56","tid":2435984,"uid":273218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T18:26:05.000Z","msg":"本地人明明係百越<br />\n但係都要扮漢人<br />\n結果粵，客，閩，壯，吳<br />\n語言不單跟北京話四川話完全不互通<br />\n而且內部亦完全不互通<br />\n但個個都自認係最正宗漢人<br />\n其實北方都保留左好多方言<br />\n跟本中國自古係自民族國家<br />\n從來無最正宗漢人"},{"pid":"ebafa38ee2500624447df6d9319a12c7cf5a4f7d","tid":2435984,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T18:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5buOsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5buOsj.jpg&h=e8418e64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17cd0b941ddf4bccf31a3a187793923f6da8bb30","tid":2435984,"uid":22701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:14:41.000Z","msg":"如果以中原地域來定義所謂中華民族，秦人已經唔係中華民族一份子，中華民族到周朝已經玩完"},{"pid":"cf07ff8e6763e98c50b578155704956e88b29921","tid":2435984,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T19:16:01.000Z","msg":"大家都是東非人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa86954e1d1e47cdbdf63b0d5e3130998a84288c","tid":2435984,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a516cfd2af15a714938ff1c990fda922545ac62b","tid":2435984,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3879801245409905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fposts%2F3879801245409905&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3f0ad4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/posts/3879801245409905</a><br />\n<br />\n由1997年至2016年期間，年報一直都話史前文化係「在本土逐漸形成，並沒有受到外來文化重大影響」；但喺2017年呢句話就消失，取而代之嘅係香港文化「同樣受到中原文化影響」。年報本來有「香港的華人只求不受干擾，故在港英政府的開明統治下，均能安居樂業。」一句，但都喺17年打後嘅版本被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgbFUET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgbFUET.png&h=b062c06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5759&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3113ca4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/ar